import HomepageTemplate from '../components/Homepage.js';
export default HomepageTemplate;

<Row className="image-card-group">
  <Column colMd={4} colLg={6} noGutterMdLeft noGutterLgLeft>
    <ImageCard
      title="Fusion HCI"
      href="/fusion-hci/overview"
      aspectRatio="16:9"
      actionIcon="launch"
      titleColor="light"
      iconColor="light"
      className="card-background"
      >

![HCI](../images/homepage/hci.jpg)

  </ImageCard>
  </Column>
  <Column colMd={4} colLg={6} noGutterMdLeft noGutterLgLeft>
    <ImageCard
        title="Fusion Software"
        href="/fusion-sds/overview"
        aspectRatio="16:9"
        actionIcon="launch"
        iconColor="light"
        titleColor="light"
        >

![SDS](../images/homepage/sds.jpg)

  </ImageCard>
  </Column>
</Row>
